şSir David Hardy
Chairman of Trustees 1995-2005
He would have been so proud that you chose to come here today
In support of Royal Museums Greenwich | rmg.co.uk/commemorate"┤
▒In memory of John Cooper Rudd (1932-95), councillor for Pepys Ward 1991-95, and Patricia Noel Anne Rudd (1932-2004), much loved, respected and missed residents of Telegraph Hill"ż
╗Major A.A.E. (Trof') Trofimov,
soldier and architect (1921-2006)
and his beloved wife, Jean Hope,
interior designer and gardener (1930-2008)
both enjoyed celebrating life to the full."ż
