┴Here is where good friends should meet
To laugh and talk on Sammy's seat
In loving memory of
Samantha Jane Thompson 1981 - 2009
She brought laughter into our lives
and love into our hearts"┘
ÍTo honour the best
Father, Philip Buchler 23.6.1972
Mother, Lisbeth Morgan 16.4.2011
Wife, Caroline Buchler 16.3.2014
A loving son and husband
David Buchler

To Honour A Dear Father
PHILIP BUCHLER
He Spent Many Happy Hours In This Sunny Garden
A Philosopher, Furrier, Worked in Mayfair & Died Too Soon
May 6th 1905 - June 23rd 1972"▄
